;; Authoritative inventory of LiGoldragon repos.
;; Supersedes the repos/ symlink index, RECENT-REPOSITORIES.md, and the
;; inventory role of protocols/active-repositories.md. A coverage or doctrine
;; run reads this file, filters lifecycle = Active, and iterates
;; /git/github.com/LiGoldragon/<name> directly; it does not depend on the
;; repos/ symlinks for membership. Editing tools resolve <name> to that path.
;;
;; Mirrors the repos/skills/manifests/*.nota convention: positional NOTA records,
;; one (Repo ...) per repo, bare atoms for canonical strings, named enum variants.
;;
;; (Repo <name> <remote> (Family <family>) <kind> <lifecycle> <doctrine-home> [<flag> ...])
;;   <name>   bare atom; canonical repo name = /git/.../LiGoldragon/<name>
;;   <remote> bare atom; github:LiGoldragon/<name>
;;   (Family <family>) grouping. signal-* repos are Signal; meta-signal-* repos
;;     are MetaSignal; every other repo groups by subsystem or cluster:
;;     Nota Schema Sema Persona Cloud DomainCriome Criome Mentci Mirror Lojix
;;     RepositoryLedger CriomOS Content Tooling.
;;   <kind> named-variant enum; what the repo *is*, orthogonal to lifecycle:
;;     Code                       source code.
;;     Content                    non-code asset (book, notes, site, config).
;;     Data                       machine-consumed data set.
;;   <lifecycle> named-variant enum; whether the repo is *kept*, orthogonal to kind:
;;     Active                     kept; wired or foundational.
;;     (Deprecated <disposition>) psyche-confirmed retirement; carries disposition.
;;   <doctrine-home> where durable direction lives (repo-intent):
;;     Architecture               has ARCHITECTURE.md.
;;     (OtherDoc <path>)          direction still homed in AGENTS.md/README.md/CLAUDE.md.
;;     (CodeStub <path>)          direction in a code comment.
;;     None                       no canonical direction surface yet (a gap to close).
;;   flags are orthogonal facts, distinct from kind and lifecycle:
;;     IsFork IsPrivate BuildTimeConsumed
;;
;; Retirement note: persona-pi, WebPublish, and AnaSeahawk-website are Deprecated
;; with disposition "remote archived + local deleted"; the psyche authorized this
;; retirement at the review gate and their local /git clones are removed.

[
